    "Name": "Blue Flame",
    "Details": "Gotta go fast? We here at QuicSell have you covered, with the blazing Blue Flame. Faster than even most lights, the only thing that can outrun it is our Blue Hedgehog. Knowing that speedy mechs often have issues targeting enemies, we've packed a pair of LBX Lasers into the turret, providing a solid chance of connecting to any target you see on the screen.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Quad Mech</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.03</color></b>",
